WEBVTT

00:01:25.385 --> 00:01:31.025
{\an8}‪ADAPTED FROM A SHUQI.COM NOVEL
‪ORIGINAL AUTHOR: SENLIN LU

00:01:36.305 --> 00:01:37.305
Your Ladyship,

00:01:38.145 --> 00:01:40.865
you're reviewing the case late at night?

00:01:43.265 --> 00:01:46.465
Can't we wait until tomorrow
to discuss it with His Majesty?

00:01:48.265 --> 00:01:49.105
Just thinking about Remonstrator Lu

00:01:49.185 --> 00:01:51.265
sleeping through the night
comfortably at home,

00:01:51.345 --> 00:01:52.545
I feel uneasy all over.

00:01:53.145 --> 00:01:54.625
So yes, sorry to trouble you both.

00:01:54.705 --> 00:01:56.705
After all, it's a case
His Majesty personally inquired about.

00:01:57.625 --> 00:01:59.265
Let's have Deputy Director Xiao
take the records.

00:02:01.105 --> 00:02:02.665
Then let's begin.

00:02:06.385 --> 00:02:07.545
Remonstrator Lu, please repeat

00:02:07.625 --> 00:02:09.465
what happened last night at Swallow House.

00:02:15.545 --> 00:02:17.545
I arrived at Swallow House
half past the You hour.

00:02:17.625 --> 00:02:19.945
I was meeting with Liu Ying'er
to go over the score.

00:02:21.345 --> 00:02:22.185
It's this section.

00:02:23.625 --> 00:02:25.345
Could you tell us again

00:02:25.425 --> 00:02:27.265
how you communicated with Liu Ying'er?

00:02:29.625 --> 00:02:31.545
That's improper.

00:02:31.625 --> 00:02:33.305
Your Ladyship,

00:02:33.385 --> 00:02:35.625
since you're handling the case this late,

00:02:35.705 --> 00:02:37.425
why not focus on the key points

00:02:37.945 --> 00:02:39.985
and resolve it quickly?

00:02:42.265 --> 00:02:43.785
What's there to be shy about?

00:02:44.505 --> 00:02:46.385
It would also give us a chance to see

00:02:46.465 --> 00:02:48.425
the talent
of the second-year graduate of Yongtai.

00:02:51.945 --> 00:02:53.185
Last night,

00:02:53.265 --> 00:02:55.745
Liu Ying'er played a new piece.

00:02:56.305 --> 00:02:58.065
I felt it lacked a bit of charm.

00:02:58.665 --> 00:03:00.865
So I composed some lyrics
for the new score.

00:03:01.465 --> 00:03:03.025
"Mist shrouds the silver boat,

00:03:04.225 --> 00:03:06.465
moon halo on the branches,
my heart grows obsessed."

00:03:07.265 --> 00:03:08.425
Nice lyrics!

00:03:09.025 --> 00:03:10.305
Truly beautiful lyrics.

00:03:10.905 --> 00:03:12.545
But I'm quite lacking in talent.

00:03:13.065 --> 00:03:15.465
Could you explain
the meaning of these words?

00:03:15.545 --> 00:03:18.425
It's just a few descriptive phrases
about the night sky.

00:03:18.505 --> 00:03:20.225
At that moment,
I glanced outside the window

00:03:20.305 --> 00:03:22.185
and saw the thick night mist
and the hazy moon halo.

00:03:22.265 --> 00:03:24.425
I casually wrote these two lines.

00:03:24.505 --> 00:03:25.905
Nothing special, really.

00:03:26.665 --> 00:03:28.505
You truly have an elegant taste.

00:03:28.585 --> 00:03:30.585
But how could such exquisite words

00:03:30.665 --> 00:03:32.745
make Liu Ying'er unhappy?

00:03:35.625 --> 00:03:38.705
I said the rhythm of the piece was off,
and it didn't match the lyrics.

00:03:38.785 --> 00:03:41.265
Liu Ying'er disagreed,
and we started arguing.

00:03:41.345 --> 00:03:44.345
At the second ke of Xu hour,
Liu Ying'er ran out in a huff.

00:03:44.425 --> 00:03:45.785
I got up to chase her,

00:03:45.865 --> 00:03:47.545
but accidentally fell down the stairs.

00:03:47.625 --> 00:03:48.985
The people in Swallow House all saw it.

00:03:49.665 --> 00:03:51.585
I really don't know anything
about Xiuhong House,

00:03:51.665 --> 00:03:52.825
and I certainly haven't been there.

00:03:52.905 --> 00:03:55.145
You two must have had quite an argument,

00:03:55.225 --> 00:03:57.185
which is why Liu Ying'er
ran out of the room.

00:03:57.265 --> 00:03:58.945
In your hurry,

00:03:59.025 --> 00:04:01.105
how did you know

00:04:01.185 --> 00:04:02.665
that it was exactly
the second ke of Xu hour?

00:04:03.465 --> 00:04:04.305
Yes.

00:04:04.905 --> 00:04:07.905
Why do you remember it so clearly?

00:04:08.545 --> 00:04:10.905
Because the attendant there

00:04:10.985 --> 00:04:12.825
was repeatedly announcing the time,

00:04:13.345 --> 00:04:15.105
"On the third day of the fifth month,
at the second ke of the Xu hour,

00:04:15.185 --> 00:04:17.225
Mr. Lu claims
'Hundred Birds Return to Nest'!"

00:04:17.305 --> 00:04:19.384
That was the most expensive reward
at Swallow House.

00:04:19.465 --> 00:04:21.265
So your lyrics were written

00:04:21.345 --> 00:04:23.265
before the second ke of Xu hour?

00:04:24.705 --> 00:04:25.745
Correct.

00:04:26.425 --> 00:04:27.785
The moon halo

00:04:28.305 --> 00:04:30.745
was also seen
before the second ke of Xu hour?

00:04:31.825 --> 00:04:33.105
Your Ladyship,

00:04:33.185 --> 00:04:36.465
why are we going back
to those lyrics again?

00:04:37.545 --> 00:04:39.425
On matters of the heavens,

00:04:39.945 --> 00:04:41.305
Deputy Director Xiao knows best.

00:04:41.385 --> 00:04:42.865
Let's ask him.

00:04:49.665 --> 00:04:51.065
According to official records,

00:04:51.145 --> 00:04:52.945
the moon halo appeared
at the fourth ke of Xu hour last night

00:04:53.025 --> 00:04:54.185
and completely dissipated by the Hai hour.

00:04:54.265 --> 00:04:56.105
If Remonstrator Lu saw the moon halo,

00:04:56.185 --> 00:04:57.305
it must have been
at the fourth ke of Xu hour.

00:04:57.905 --> 00:04:59.465
After you wrote the lyrics, argued,

00:04:59.545 --> 00:05:00.945
then fell down the stairs,

00:05:01.025 --> 00:05:02.305
that would've been
at least the sixth ke of Xu hour.

00:05:06.305 --> 00:05:07.865
So, you're lying.

00:05:08.825 --> 00:05:10.545
No, I'm not!

00:05:10.625 --> 00:05:11.945
Everyone, think about it.

00:05:12.025 --> 00:05:14.385
If it wasn't for that attendant
shouting out the second ke of Xu hour,

00:05:14.465 --> 00:05:15.945
how would I know the exact time?

00:05:16.025 --> 00:05:18.225
I arrived at Swallow House
half past the You hour

00:05:18.305 --> 00:05:19.665
to meet Liu Ying'er.

00:05:19.745 --> 00:05:21.105
And I really did see the moon halo.

00:05:21.185 --> 00:05:24.385
If someone is lying,
it should be the attendant.

00:05:24.465 --> 00:05:26.065
Why blame me for it?

00:05:26.145 --> 00:05:27.865
There was no water clock at Swallow House.

00:05:28.465 --> 00:05:30.385
The time was reported
by the nearby watchman.

00:05:30.985 --> 00:05:32.345
If he was in your pocket,

00:05:32.425 --> 00:05:34.105
- the hour was yours to name.
- You…

00:05:34.185 --> 00:05:35.745
With a few coins,

00:05:35.825 --> 00:05:38.465
you bought any time you pleased.

00:05:39.345 --> 00:05:40.905
Speaking nonsense!

00:05:40.985 --> 00:05:42.785
Am I speaking nonsense?

00:05:42.865 --> 00:05:44.585
Once the watchman arrives, we'll know.

00:05:45.585 --> 00:05:46.625
Don't rush.

00:05:46.705 --> 00:05:48.185
We've already caught him.

00:05:48.265 --> 00:05:49.105
He should be here soon.

00:05:51.225 --> 00:05:52.265
Remonstrator Lu,

00:05:53.225 --> 00:05:55.985
Her Ladyship has seen you
at Xiuhong House.

00:05:56.065 --> 00:05:57.985
Can't you be wronged?

00:05:58.065 --> 00:06:00.905
Rather than trying to scheme your way out,

00:06:00.985 --> 00:06:03.625
a honest confession serves you better!

00:06:04.425 --> 00:06:05.585
Alright.

00:06:09.385 --> 00:06:10.545
This case

00:06:10.625 --> 00:06:14.745
involves the inner palace.
It's a serious matter.

00:06:15.345 --> 00:06:17.385
The Court of Judicial Review will assist
the Palace Investigation Bureau

00:06:17.465 --> 00:06:19.065
in investigating it.

00:06:19.665 --> 00:06:21.265
As for Lu Zhenglian,

00:06:21.345 --> 00:06:23.865
once I report it tomorrow,

00:06:24.585 --> 00:06:26.425
His Majesty will decide.

00:06:27.025 --> 00:06:27.905
Understood.

00:06:46.985 --> 00:06:48.305
Prosecutor Gu has found Jiang Tingwei.

00:06:48.385 --> 00:06:49.825
We're short on manpower
and need reinforcements.

00:06:53.705 --> 00:06:54.985
Chief Justice.

00:06:57.985 --> 00:06:59.705
I'll leave Remonstrator Lu to you.

00:07:00.905 --> 00:07:01.745
Understood.

00:07:26.345 --> 00:07:28.105
If we do nothing,

00:07:28.185 --> 00:07:30.865
we'll have no way out.

00:07:43.385 --> 00:07:44.665
Everyone, be sharp.

00:07:44.745 --> 00:07:45.585
Strengthen the defenses.

00:07:45.665 --> 00:07:46.905
